queries.query: INSERT INTO `users` (`vFirstName`, `vLastName`, `vUserName`, `vEmail`, `vMobileNo`, `dDob`, `tAddress`, `vCity`, `dLatitude`, `dLongitude`, `iStateId`, `vStateName`, `vZipCode`, `eStatus`, `dtAddedAt`, `dtUpdatedAt`, `eDeviceType`, `vDeviceModel`, `vDeviceOS`, `vDeviceToken`, `vEmailVerificationCode`, `vAccessToken`, `eSocialLoginType`, `vSocialLoginId`, `eEmailVerified`, `vTermsConditionsVersion`, `vPrivacyPolicyVersion`) VALUES ('test', 'cust5', 'user5', 'cust5@dd.in', '9566669895', '', '205,panchmi heights', 'pune', '', '', '', 'maharashtra', '411312', 'Inactive', NOW(), '', 'android', 'moto e4 plus', 'android', '', '', '846553795e194edf970df20b83699e8ea5f0db5b38fe92d87a3357f80ae8a427', 'gmail', 'cust5@gmail.com', 'Yes', '1.0', '1.0')

SELECT `u`.`vFirstName` AS `u_first_name`,`u`.`iUserId` AS `u_user_id`,`u`.`vLastName` AS `u_last_name`,`u`.`vUserName` AS `u_user_name`,`u`.`vEmail` AS `u_email`,`u`.`vMobileNo` AS `u_mobile_no`,`u`.`vProfileImage` AS `u_profile_image`,`u`.`dDob` AS `u_dob`,`u`.`tAddress` AS `u_address`,`u`.`vCity` AS `u_city`,`u`.`dLatitude` AS `u_latitude`,`u`.`dLongitude` AS `u_longitude`,`u`.`iStateId` AS `u_state_id`,`u`.`vStateName` AS `u_state_name`,`u`.`vZipCode` AS `u_zip_code`,`u`.`eStatus` AS `u_status`,(concat(u.vFirstName,' ',u.vLastName)) AS email_user_name,`u`.`eEmailVerified` AS `u_email_verified`,`u`.`vAccessToken` AS `u_access_token`,`u`.`eDeviceType` AS `u_device_type`,`u`.`vDeviceModel` AS `u_device_model`,`u`.`vDeviceOS` AS `u_device_os`,`u`.`vDeviceToken` AS `u_device_token`,`u`.`dtAddedAt` AS `u_added_at`,`u`.`eSocialLoginType` AS `u_social_login_type`,`u`.`vSocialLoginId` AS `u_social_login_id`,`u`.`eOneTimeTransaction` AS `e_one_time_transaction`,`u`.`tOneTimeTransaction` AS `t_one_time_transaction`,`u`.`ePushNotify` AS `u_push_notify`,`u`.`vTermsConditionsVersion` AS `terms_conditions_version`,`u`.`vPrivacyPolicyVersion` AS `privacy_policy_version`,`u`.`eLogStatus` AS `u_log_status_updated` FROM `users` AS `u` WHERE `u`.`iUserId` = 220  LIMIT 1
